<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3042826" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">当然不算抄袭了，现在都有时尚品牌用JoJo做广告：<br><br><noscript><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/7893fe6379fff3321bf261a8b6b130da_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="530" data-rawheight="450" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="530" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/7893fe6379fff3321bf261a8b6b130da_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="530" data-rawheight="450" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="530" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/7893fe6379fff3321bf261a8b6b130da_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic3.zhimg.com/7893fe6379fff3321bf261a8b6b130da_b.jpg"><br><noscript><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/54873ea50aa981367b7c2f82bff94b78_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="606" data-rawheight="420" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="606" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/54873ea50aa981367b7c2f82bff94b78_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="606" data-rawheight="420" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="606" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/54873ea50aa981367b7c2f82bff94b78_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic1.zhimg.com/54873ea50aa981367b7c2f82bff94b78_b.jpg"><br>我的乔斯达，时尚时尚最时尚。<br><br><br>再者，JoJo参考时尚杂志，主要是集中在动作上：<br><noscript><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/bf4dd4e05145376e4c95129d109ef86a_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="423" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/bf4dd4e05145376e4c95129d109ef86a_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="423" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="600" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/bf4dd4e05145376e4c95129d109ef86a_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic3.zhimg.com/bf4dd4e05145376e4c95129d109ef86a_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/3420c7c2b7c3f46556d1f61e45286bf5_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="511" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/3420c7c2b7c3f46556d1f61e45286bf5_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="511" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="600" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/3420c7c2b7c3f46556d1f61e45286bf5_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic2.zhimg.com/3420c7c2b7c3f46556d1f61e45286bf5_b.jpg"><br>而其中人物的服装，则完全是荒木自己设计的。<br><br><br>反观新田佑克，连衣服都画的几乎一样：<br><noscript><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/4146b0a855c8a84ed94564b5a17d826c_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="896" data-rawheight="637" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="896" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/4146b0a855c8a84ed94564b5a17d826c_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="896" data-rawheight="637" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="896" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/4146b0a855c8a84ed94564b5a17d826c_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic1.zhimg.com/4146b0a855c8a84ed94564b5a17d826c_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/38045dfb9366355dcd54fccf1f8691ab_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="560" data-rawheight="419" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="560" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/38045dfb9366355dcd54fccf1f8691ab_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="560" data-rawheight="419" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="560" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/38045dfb9366355dcd54fccf1f8691ab_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic4.zhimg.com/38045dfb9366355dcd54fccf1f8691ab_b.jpg">


