<a data-tip="p$t$gc417893929" href="/people/gc417893929">张行</a>，<strong title="本来无一物 何处惹尘埃" class="zu-question-my-bio">本来无一物 何处惹尘埃</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
