<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="88">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$chen-yan-kun" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/chen-yan-kun" class="zg-link" title="BinarySCV">BinarySCV</a>、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$kun-aaa" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/kun-aaa" class="zg-link" title="kun aaa">kun aaa</a></span>
