<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3042826" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">补 <a data-hash="59fcae62596fb6ba08f2860a5fe6f171" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/59fcae62596fb6ba08f2860a5fe6f171" class="member_mention" data-editable="true" data-title="@Kaiser" data-tip="p$b$59fcae62596fb6ba08f2860a5fe6f171">@Kaiser</a> 几张图<br><br><b>2013年伊始古驰 (Gucci) 
把人气漫画《JOJO奇妙冒险》请进了全球近八十家品牌精品店的橱窗，向顾客展示出奢侈品牌也可以有“不拘一格”的时髦态度。橱窗中展示的漫画是《JOJO奇妙冒险》的作者荒木飞吕彦为古驰 
(Gucci) 创作的特别短篇，画风华丽、个性鲜明，意大利奢侈品牌古驰 (Gucci) 
选择与这部人气漫画合作，各位报友觉得是“很诡异”还是“有眼光”呢？下定论之前，先一起来欣赏下橱窗中展示的漫画《徐伦，飞向Gucci》的精彩图片吧！ </b><br><br><br><b><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/0903c2183a8a29908eeb1298ec66e7ba_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="580" data-rawheight="397" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="580" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/0903c2183a8a29908eeb1298ec66e7ba_r.jpg"><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/64d4ea5926a69b7e02a88c6056b2f291_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="580" data-rawheight="812" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="580" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/64d4ea5926a69b7e02a88c6056b2f291_r.jpg"><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/821b5a7b82d8415dd0c977fcc20b7a3a_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="580" data-rawheight="828" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="580" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/821b5a7b82d8415dd0c977fcc20b7a3a_r.jpg"><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/63ff61586641397e201050668c9471b3_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="580" data-rawheight="895" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="580" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/63ff61586641397e201050668c9471b3_r.jpg"><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/37f61c9611e068305c18206171e8f8a0_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="580" data-rawheight="882" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="580" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/37f61c9611e068305c18206171e8f8a0_r.jpg"><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/ccee4786a5d9317d1fc0d1e05fd9f96c_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="580" data-rawheight="834" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="580" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/ccee4786a5d9317d1fc0d1e05fd9f96c_r.jpg"><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/547d416e04794730a14bd3ac5071f9ac_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="580" data-rawheight="893" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="580" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/547d416e04794730a14bd3ac5071f9ac_r.jpg"><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/99882f83fc06a574574c28ed70794aac_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="580" data-rawheight="899" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="580" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/99882f83fc06a574574c28ed70794aac_r.jpg"><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/182cbec201a1baeeddbc2c740f1c0851_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="580" data-rawheight="892" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="580" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/182cbec201a1baeeddbc2c740f1c0851_r.jpg">后边的还有些，见<a href="http://tieba.baidu.com/p/2081343957" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">【简体汉化】徐伦、飞向GUCCI_jojo奇妙冒险吧<i class="icon-external"></i></a><br><br>服装风格相当华丽</b><br><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/c55135dd896c8dd6c7d56366fec676d3_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="788" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/c55135dd896c8dd6c7d56366fec676d3_r.jpg"><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/5c9750f47b9a766eb18cfc4861a8ddde_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="450" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/5c9750f47b9a766eb18cfc4861a8ddde_r.jpg"><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/04b5e5a6ca6f636ac2d0f93ab516b749_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="852" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/04b5e5a6ca6f636ac2d0f93ab516b749_r.jpg"><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/f2c1a5d9f540f109ee4377b9a9fd9fdd_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="870" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/f2c1a5d9f540f109ee4377b9a9fd9fdd_r.jpg"><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/25160dfd4361a71150dcbb58302e0d9e_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="850" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/25160dfd4361a71150dcbb58302e0d9e_r.jpg"><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/7f48520d6c1c72abecb5a479114d663f_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="854" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/7f48520d6c1c72abecb5a479114d663f_r.jpg"><br><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/5d29c455e61f6593cbddcb1e103a4286_b.jpg" data-rawwidth=